Package org.jtool.cfg

Class JReference

java.lang.Object
org.jtool.cfg.JReference
Direct Known Subclasses:
JFieldReference, JLocalVarReference, JMethodReference, JSpecialVarReference
public abstract class JReference
extends java.lang.Object
An abstract class that represents a reference to a field, a local variable, or a method.
